transcription: The sexual marketplace is a complex dynamic. There are people who have massive advantages and massive disadvantages. There are people who lucked into being in social scenes or having mentorship, which meant that they learned how to do this early on. And so it becomes part of their confidence, part of their lifestyle, part of the thing that they just do. And for many men, that doesn't happen because of isolation, because of the fact that they were shy, because they didn't have any older brothers to show them or older sisters or women in their life in general to get used to being around women, because of computer games, because of the internet, because of the atomization of societies in general.
